ultimately how these pathologies evolve and combine to cause clinical
consequences.</td><td>Tissue-imaging analysis of individual lesions is needed to understand
pathological mechanisms.</td></tr><tr><td>Make better use of existing cohort data</td><td>Study registration and public availability of protocols would
